The woman mentions that it's an aphrodisiac. The man questions by whom [assuming who had mentioned that to be the case]. The woman, startled by his question, responds, \"people...\" ", "importance": "5", "time": 218484, "tag": "test_seg2_desc"}

She mentions something about quick sex, wanting it? He lights up a cigarette, which she despises, removing it from his lips and ashes it on a nearby ashtray. Her partner lights another one up quickly. Noting his demeanour, she makes her way to him, removing the second cigarette, apologizing, and consoles him, saying that she didn't mean to do what she did. She does so in a seductive manner, later reaching to his neck which appears to be an on/off switch. ", "importance": "6", "time": 451353, "tag": "test_seg4_desc"}

The woman mentions one that is more sporty or adventurous, looking on her laptop screen one model that is a rock-climber or a male masseuse. ", "importance": "5", "time": 343112, "tag": "test_seg6_desc"}
